    {
      "assetId": "math.arith.fraction-equivalence/teaching_note/3",
      "kind": "teaching_note",
      "conceptId": "math.arith.fraction-equivalence",
      "title": "Prerequisite Check",
      "content": "Run PRE-1 before Protocol A (S0 entry). If gap detected, halt and address prerequisite first.\n\n---\n\n**PRE-1 — Fraction Concept** (requires math.arith.fractions)\n\nStimulus: \"What does the fraction 3/5 mean? What does the denominator 5 tell you?\"\n\nExpected: 3 parts out of 5 equal parts (or equivalent phrasing)\n\nSIGNAL:INCORRECT → prerequisite gap: math.arith.fractions; schedule that session before returning\n\n---\n\n**PRE-2 — Integer Multiplication**\n\nStimulus: \"What is 4 × 7?\"\n\nExpected: 28\n\nSIGNAL:INCORRECT → prerequisite arithmetic gap; address multiplication before this session\n\n---",
      "localKey": null,
